\n<\N[13]>If you struggle hard enough for me...\.\. I might

With the clacking of the giant goth's teeth shutting out all
the light, you immediately find yourself set upon by the indomitable tongue.\.\.
Subdued by the massive, powerful beast, you're completely at the mercy of
\N[13]'s cravings, and you are soon treated to the complete experience of becoming food.
You're brutally tossed, tasted, licked, and sloshed around every corner
of the giantess's mouth as she savours you like the most
succulent morsel she's ever devoured.\.\. Pizza-infused breath bakes you,
and salt and vinegar laced saliva threatens to drown you.
You're subjected to the experience of being mere candy for the
selfish girl for what feels like an eternity.\.\. In reality, it's only
...Before her stomach's greed gets the best of her urges.
Unfortunately for you, it seems she never really had any
intention of letting you back out.\.\. With a long, drawn out

Caught up in a wave of pizza flavoured saliva, you slip with
astonishing ease straight into the giant girl's esophagus.\.\.
You slide down the slimy, endless tunnel of flesh as easily as every other
piece of food to take the journey before you.
Waves of muscular contractions force you down, the sounds of
\N[13]'s impatient stomach growing closer and closer as the
girl's kneading throat delivers you effortlessly into the depths of her belly.
Just as the constricting throat muscles and overbearing saliva
are starting to become too much, you're finally dumped into the
churning cauldron of the girl's stomach, straight into a deep pool of
\N[13], having not even the slightest intention of releasing you, massages her
midriff while basking in an unrivaled sense of satisfaction.\.\.
Meanwhile, you prepare yourself for the prolonged agony of being slowly
digested, alone in the simmering darkness of the gothic girl's stomach.
